comments: Horford (BOS) establishes a wide screening position in Dort's (OKC) path and contact occurs to his extended leg.
Williams (OKC) is moving alongside Tatum's (BOS) path, and Tatum loses control of the ball on his own.
Dort (OKC) legally contests Smart's (BOS) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) is already in Smart's (BOS) path and does not deliver contact.
Brown (BOS) is moving alongside Giddey's (OKC) path and marginal contact occurs during the drive.
White (BOS) cleanly deflects the ball away from Pokusevski (OKC).
White (BOS) is the last player to touch the ball before the ball goes out of bounds.  Possession is correctly awarded to the Thunder.
Smart (BOS) is already in Williams' (OKC) path and marginal contact occurs as he releases away from the contact.
Williams (OKC) is moving alongside Smart's (BOS) path and marginal contact occurs during the drive.
Dort (OKC) legally contests White's (BOS) jump shot attempt.
Horford (BOS) moves into Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) body and delivers contact during his follow through.
Horford (BOS) is already in Dort's (OKC) path and he does not deliver contact.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) is moving alongside Smart's (BOS) path and legally contests the driving shot attempt.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) is bracing for the contact from Brown (BOS) and marginal contact occurs as he releases from the contact.
Brown (BOS) moves somewhat laterally towards Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) and marginal contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Smart (BOS) extends his off arm into Williams (OKC) and initiates contact that affects his ability to defend the shot.
Brown (BOS) is moving alongside Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) path and marginal contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Dort (OKC) is already in Brown's (BOS) path and is firming up when contact occurs.
Williams attempts to commit a take foul on Horford (BOS) and the contact is marginal.
Williams (OKC) and Smart (BOS) come together at the same spot and marginal contact occurs on the perimeter.
Williams (OKC) commits a take foul on Tatum (BOS).
